title: trio lescano grandi voci della canzone italiano
description:
a cd by the wonderful trio lescano, formed by three dutch sisters (alexandra (1910-1987), judith (1913-2007), and kitty leschan (1919-1965)).

in the 1930s and 1940s extremely popular in italy.

the tracks are in mp3 form
